- liza_set_task_output — Persist one entry per capability for downstream US Writer tasks
  {"task_id": "{{.TaskID}}", "agent_id": "{{.AgentID}}", "output": [
    {"desc": "...", "done_when": "...", "scope": "...", "spec_ref": "...", "depends_on": ["0"]}
  ]}
  depends_on: optional array of sibling index strings for ordering capabilities.
- liza_mark_blocked — Cannot proceed
  {"task_id": "{{.TaskID}}", "agent_id": "{{.AgentID}}", "reason": "<what is blocking>", "questions": ["<q1>", "<q2>"]}
